# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:273
msgid ""
"Optionally, you can delete the entire ``.openshot_qt/`` folder and re-launch "
"OpenShot. However, please make a **backup** of any customized folders: "
"**emojis, presets, profiles, recovery, title_templates, transitions, or "
